  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you hit a creature with a weapon attack or unarmed strike, you can expend one superiority die to attempt to disarm the target, forcing it to drop one item of your choice that it's holding. You add the superiority die to the attack's damage roll, and the target must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save, it drops the object you choose. The object lands in the space of your choice within 10 feet of the enemy.</p>",
